ğŸ¥­ Component 2
Mango Quality Grading System for Export

AI-Based Ripeness Detection â€¢ Size Measurement â€¢ Weight Measurement (GAP Compliance)

Welcome to the Mango Quality Grading System, a low-cost computer vision and deep learningâ€“based research project designed to automatically grade Alphonso (TJC) mangoes for export quality.

This system replaces subjective human inspection with an objective, repeatable, and consistent AI-driven approach using images captured from a simple setup.

Quality Parameters

âœ… Ripeness stage
âœ… Physical size
âœ… Weight

Final output determines whether a mango is export quality (GAP compliant) or rejected.

ğŸ¯ Research Motivation

Traditional mango grading for export is:

